      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a mechanic, restorer, or anyone looking for a donor car for parts. The engine is currently not running and will require significant diagnostic work or a complete rebuild to become roadworthy again. Externally, the body shows heavy wear, including noticeable rust patches, several large dents, and peeling clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is torn in multiple places and the electronics are largely unresponsive, making this a true project car for someone with the right tools and time.",
