    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist's specification featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. The naturally aspirated power plant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to reach its 8,400 RPM redline with surgical throttle response. The chassis is sharpened by Electronic Damping Control (EDC) and a variable M Differential Lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip and turn-in precision. It has been maintained with a focus on longevity, including a proactive rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators. The hydraulic steering rack offers the communicative feedback modern EPS systems lack, making this a definitive driver\u2019s machine.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
