      "description": "Presented in commendable condition, this vehicle exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Meticulously maintained to rigorous standards, it offers a refined driving experience characterized by reliability and sophistication. An exceptional acquisition for the discerning driver seeking both value and performance.",
      "price": 36800.0,
