      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s looking for a new home! It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in great shape, perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. It drives like a dream and has been really well-cared for. I'm sad to see it go, but I know you'll love it as much as I have. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
