      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine paired with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanical highlights include a recently serviced VANOS system and reinforced rear subframe mounts, addressing key platform requirements. The limited-slip differential provides excellent power delivery out of corners, while the chassis remains composed with responsive steering feedback. Well-maintained and ready for the enthusiast who values powertrain integrity and iconic performance over a museum-grade shelf life.",
